node.title: Wildest celebrity fashion
node.description: Celebrities have been stepping out in wild outfits for years... some more often than others.
node.content: ["For years, the coronavirus pandemic effectively shut down Hollywood's red carpets \u2014 but the tide may be turning. 2022 has already seen some daring fashion looks via the Screen Actors Guild Awards, the BAFTAs and more than one wild look via live concerts. Even 2021, with its COVID-19-affected, stop-and-start schedules, managed to serve up a few bold fashion moments.", "Here are some of the most outr\u00e9 celebrity looks we've seen.", "Here, Hailee Steinfeld attends the 28th Screen Actors Guild Awards in Santa Monica, California, on February 27, 2022.", "The \"Dickinson\" star graced the red carpet in a gleaming black dress by Miu Miu \u2014 a custom number featuring a push-up-bra-inspired bodice."]
